data.description: Beautiful home with a pool in Bullard! Convenient to Hwy 69 for easy access to both Tyler and Jacksonville. Spacious living room and two dining areas. Primary suite has a spacious en suite with soaking tub, walk-in shower, and dual vanities. Three guest rooms share a hall bath. Enjoy summertime in and around the sparkling pool and cabana! Quiet location at the end of a street. See this one soon!
